# EDITORIAL DESIGN SYSTEM PROMPT FOR TOPIC PAGES

## CRITICAL DESIGN RULES - FOLLOW EXACTLY

### Typography System
```typescript
// ALWAYS use these exact font classes from your Tailwind config:

font-heading  // For all H1, H2, H3 headings (Larken font)
font-body     // For all paragraphs, descriptions (Crimson Text)
font-ui       // For labels, categories, metadata (General Sans)
```

### Color System
```typescript
// ONLY use these brand colors - NO custom colors allowed:

bg-background           // Page backgrounds (#f9fafb)
text-foreground         // Primary text (#252220)
text-foreground/70      // Secondary text (70% opacity)
text-foreground/60      // Tertiary text (60% opacity)
border-foreground/10    // Section dividers (10% opacity)
border-foreground/30    // Interactive borders (30% opacity)
bg-foreground/5         // Subtle background boxes (5% opacity)
```

### Layout Structure

**Container Widths:**
- Main article content: `max-w-4xl` (narrower for readability)
- Full-width sections: `max-w-7xl`
- Always use: `mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`

**Vertical Spacing:**
- Main sections: `mb-20` (80px gap between major sections)
- Subsections: `mb-16` (64px)
- Paragraphs: `mb-12` (48px)
- Between elements: `mb-8` or `mb-6`
- Top padding for sections: `pt-12`

